{"ja370:0.1":"Jataka ","ja370:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","ja370:0.3":"Vannarohavagga ","ja370:0.4":"10. Palasajataka ","ja370:1.1":"“Hamso palasamavaca, ","ja370:1.2":"nigrodho samma jayati; ","ja370:1.3":"Ankasmim te nisinnova, ","ja370:1.4":"so te mammani checchati”. ","ja370:2.1":"“Vaddhatameva nigrodho, ","ja370:2.2":"patitthassa bhavamaham; ","ja370:2.3":"Yatha pita ca mata ca, ","ja370:2.4":"evam me so bhavissati”. ","ja370:3.1":"“Yam tvam ankasmim vaddhesi, ","ja370:3.2":"khirarukkham bhayanakam; ","ja370:3.3":"Amanta kho tam gacchama, ","ja370:3.4":"vuddhi massa na ruccati”. ","ja370:4.1":"“Idani kho mam bhayeti, ","ja370:4.2":"mahanerunidassanam; ","ja370:4.3":"Hamsassa anabhinnaya, ","ja370:4.4":"maha me bhayamagatam”. ","ja370:5.1":"“Na tassa vuddhi kusalappasattha, ","ja370:5.2":"Yo vaddhamano ghasate patittham; ","ja370:5.3":"Tassuparodham parisankamano, ","ja370:5.4":"Patarayi mulavadhaya dhiro”ti. ","ja370:6.1":"Palasajatakam dasamam. ","ja370:6.2":"Vannarohavaggo dutiyo. "}